      • getReferencedComponentType

        public short getReferencedComponentType()
        Calculates referenced component type by invoking SnomedTerminologyComponentConstants.getTerminologyComponentIdValue(String) with the member's referenced component identifier. Assumes that getReferencedComponentId() returns a valid SNOMED CT component id. If this is not the case (particularly with mapping reference set members), subclasses should override.
        Specified by:
        getReferencedComponentType in interface SnomedRefSetMember
        Returns:
        the application specific terminology component type of the referenced component.
